{"tid":2186953,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"自製日式大阪燒「附自製大阪燒醬汁」","createTime":"2020-09-03T10:16:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T15:59:21.000Z","uid":68594,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ce29d436f5c1f0e35009d518416d8a393834da0a","tid":2186953,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:16:16.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係子言張<br />\n<br />\n我終於搵返份工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />少左時間上來找數<br />\n<br />\n我突然之間有一日心血來潮好想食大阪燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係靈魂所在就係佢個<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">醬汁</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n仆街係一田嗰啲買成20$-30$支，仲要唔係成日用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n把心一橫，決定都係自己整<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NgRHfQF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNgRHfQF.png&h=3b6814e0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SAw4uaL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSAw4uaL.png&h=fe7946d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料 (2個大阪燒份量)<br />\n(如只需製作一個大阪燒，請將以下份量全部減半)<br />\n椰菜.....半個<br />\n甘筍.....半條<br />\n洋蔥.....半個<br />\n京蔥.....1條<br />\n麵粉.....250克<br />\n雞蛋.....2隻<br />\n煙肉.....3塊<br />\n蝦.......10隻<br />\n<br />\n調味料<br />\n日式沙律醬、濃縮鰹魚汁、浙江醋、燒肉汁、鰹魚碎、胡椒粉、鹽、糖、生粉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LzehPaN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLzehPaN.png&h=57396fad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雞蛋打到大碗內，倒入250克麵粉、一匙鹽、一湯匙濃縮鰹魚汁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e5gDyCw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe5gDyCw.png&h=4b86e54d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nYoZh4e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnYoZh4e.png&h=084b56aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n準備一杯清水，一邊攪拌一邊倒入清水，今次約需兩杯半左右清水，攪拌至流質狀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5vdynvX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5vdynvX.png&h=792868a8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZGH3KKn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZGH3KKn.png&h=65fa0524&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NWAXPa8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNWAXPa8.png&h=1b67b307&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n椰菜切碎、甘筍切粒、洋蔥切粒，倒入漿內並撈勻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g7P2fRe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg7P2fRe.png&h=ef126991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨個人喜好加入其他配料(如京蔥、蝦、墨魚等)煙肉切成片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RmAkMXX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRmAkMXX.png&h=5ba76438&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n倒入80ml燒肉汁、40ml濃縮鰹魚汁、20ml浙江醋到鍋裡，開火加熱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AXsOVRP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAXsOVRP.png&h=0cf09c49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n滾起後倒入兩匙砂糖、80-100ml清水，再開火煮滾，完全滾起後關火，然後倒入生粉水。醬汁能掛在匙羮上即可<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y8NLdDx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY8NLdDx.png&h=ddc325bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.冷鑊落油，油熱後倒入大阪燒漿，大約煎兩至三分鐘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FpGLX5g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFpGLX5g.png&h=a74e43d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在大阪燒上鋪上煙肉片，轉細火，冚蓋煎5-6分鐘<br />\n開蓋後把大阪燒翻面，冚蓋煎5-6分鐘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r5GW4Lk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr5GW4Lk.png&h=f8356d76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開蓋後，用筷子試一試大阪燒內是否熟透<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cmGPFiK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcmGPFiK.png&h=ba96b1ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再把大阪燒翻面把表面煎脆，多煎4-5分鐘後上碟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXRzRqs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXRzRqs.png&h=bd616869&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oSxrHxb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoSxrHxb.png&h=96fa41c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nspqdDW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnspqdDW.png&h=772c763c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n淋上大阪燒醬汁、沙律醬、青蔥、木魚花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><br />\n</span></span>完成！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鍾意我呢段片嘅朋友可以俾個like我啦或者可以訂閱我嘅Channel嘅！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0efa35116da84ebff34116af497646aca4e942","tid":2186953,"uid":68594,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:27:39.000Z","msg":"最後附上影片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/U9X02MqTVNA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FU9X02MqTVNA&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3heL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=cf586aff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/U9X02MqTVNA</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家鐘意啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72bb408560f09b6da15ad2f68e183b0f74aa580e","tid":2186953,"uid":1366,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:29:00.000Z","msg":"哇咁多野要買，出街買算<br />\n支持言巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e863c3237e34dd920cc8e3fc23b7aa4e2821d7","tid":2186953,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"72bb408560f09b6da15ad2f68e183b0f74aa580e","tid":2186953,"uid":1366,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:29:00.000Z","msg":"哇咁多野要買，出街買算<br />\n支持言巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:30:41.000Z","msg":"唔算多又唔算少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />懶又唔想行咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝醉巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5457996410031a4df60ab7b9bec415e205c085e","tid":2186953,"uid":75583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:59:18.000Z","msg":"我都整過，個汁用味醂 浙醋 糖 水 日本豉油 蠔油 茄汁撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee1321fe7cdd91781d0477f1c5cb268fad0dd24c","tid":2186953,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d5457996410031a4df60ab7b9bec415e205c085e","tid":2186953,"uid":75583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:59:18.000Z","msg":"我都整過，個汁用味醂 浙醋 糖 水 日本豉油 蠔油 茄汁撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T11:01:00.000Z","msg":"應該都幾似<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df74bffe77a3bc03bea59fcf07b31c8b6624213d","tid":2186953,"uid":75583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ee1321fe7cdd91781d0477f1c5cb268fad0dd24c","tid":2186953,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d5457996410031a4df60ab7b9bec415e205c085e","tid":2186953,"uid":75583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:59:18.000Z","msg":"我都整過，個汁用味醂 浙醋 糖 水 日本豉油 蠔油 茄汁撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T11:01:00.000Z","msg":"應該都幾似<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T11:07:05.000Z","msg":"冇你果個整得咁靚！講起又想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ef8e108555ae84d452a9e9aab506bb90aa4fcc","tid":2186953,"uid":54415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T14:33:24.000Z","msg":"推下言巴先"},{"pid":"aac0176ff417ed1c0f02b7a08a2ca9be8f8fea73","tid":2186953,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T14:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好有心機整"},{"pid":"db9fe0a43be14b995643019684dff1cbc6bba409","tid":2186953,"uid":128961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ce29d436f5c1f0e35009d518416d8a393834da0a","tid":2186953,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:16:16.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係子言張<br />\n<br />\n我終於搵返份工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />少左時間上來找數<br />\n<br />\n我突然之間有一日心血來潮好想食大阪燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係靈魂所在就係佢個<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">醬汁</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n仆街係一田嗰啲買成20$-30$支，仲要唔係成日用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n把心一橫，決定都係自己整<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NgRHfQF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNgRHfQF.png&h=3b6814e0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SAw4uaL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSAw4uaL.png&h=fe7946d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料 (2個大阪燒份量)<br />\n(如只需製作一個大阪燒，請將以下份量全部減半)<br />\n椰菜.....半個<br />\n甘筍.....半條<br />\n洋蔥.....半個<br />\n京蔥.....1條<br />\n麵粉.....250克<br />\n雞蛋.....2隻<br />\n煙肉.....3塊<br />\n蝦.......10隻<br />\n<br />\n調味料<br />\n日式沙律醬、濃縮鰹魚汁、浙江醋、燒肉汁、鰹魚碎、胡椒粉、鹽、糖、生粉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LzehPaN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLzehPaN.png&h=57396fad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雞蛋打到大碗內，倒入250克麵粉、一匙鹽、一湯匙濃縮鰹魚汁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e5gDyCw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe5gDyCw.png&h=4b86e54d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nYoZh4e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnYoZh4e.png&h=084b56aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n準備一杯清水，一邊攪拌一邊倒入清水，今次約需兩杯半左右清水，攪拌至流質狀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5vdynvX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5vdynvX.png&h=792868a8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZGH3KKn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZGH3KKn.png&h=65fa0524&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NWAXPa8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNWAXPa8.png&h=1b67b307&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n椰菜切碎、甘筍切粒、洋蔥切粒，倒入漿內並撈勻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g7P2fRe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg7P2fRe.png&h=ef126991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨個人喜好加入其他配料(如京蔥、蝦、墨魚等)煙肉切成片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RmAkMXX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRmAkMXX.png&h=5ba76438&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n倒入80ml燒肉汁、40ml濃縮鰹魚汁、20ml浙江醋到鍋裡，開火加熱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AXsOVRP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAXsOVRP.png&h=0cf09c49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n滾起後倒入兩匙砂糖、80-100ml清水，再開火煮滾，完全滾起後關火，然後倒入生粉水。醬汁能掛在匙羮上即可<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y8NLdDx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY8NLdDx.png&h=ddc325bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.冷鑊落油，油熱後倒入大阪燒漿，大約煎兩至三分鐘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FpGLX5g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFpGLX5g.png&h=a74e43d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在大阪燒上鋪上煙肉片，轉細火，冚蓋煎5-6分鐘<br />\n開蓋後把大阪燒翻面，冚蓋煎5-6分鐘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r5GW4Lk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr5GW4Lk.png&h=f8356d76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開蓋後，用筷子試一試大阪燒內是否熟透<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cmGPFiK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcmGPFiK.png&h=ba96b1ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再把大阪燒翻面把表面煎脆，多煎4-5分鐘後上碟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXRzRqs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXRzRqs.png&h=bd616869&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oSxrHxb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoSxrHxb.png&h=96fa41c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nspqdDW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnspqdDW.png&h=772c763c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n淋上大阪燒醬汁、沙律醬、青蔥、木魚花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><br />\n</span></span>完成！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鍾意我呢段片嘅朋友可以俾個like我啦或者可以訂閱我嘅Channel嘅！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T14:44:42.000Z","msg":"建議加埋准山泥，口感再好食啲"},{"pid":"56919c68b99a38938012303f7ed1f75e2b1fe960","tid":2186953,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db9fe0a43be14b995643019684dff1cbc6bba409","tid":2186953,"uid":128961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ce29d436f5c1f0e35009d518416d8a393834da0a","tid":2186953,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:16:16.000Z","msg":"大家好，我